'''恒天然合作社集团有限公司'''（{{Lang-en|'''Fonterra Co-operative Group Limited'''}}），简称'''恒天然'''，是[[新西兰|新西兰]]一家由約10,500位當地[[農民|農民]]經營的的[[跨國公司|跨國]][[奶制品|乳製品]][[合作社|合作社]]<ref name="AnnRpt2012">{{cite web |url = http://www2.fonterra.com/our-co-op |title = Fonterra Website |date = 5 September 2016 |author = Fonterra Co-operative Group |format = HTML |publisher =  |website =  |access-date = 5 September 2016 |archive-date = 2016-10-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161016162852/http://www2.fonterra.com/our-co-op |dead-url = no }}</ref>。該公司現佔有全球乳製品出口量約30%<ref name="NBR_103322">{{cite news|url = http://www.nbr.co.nz/article/nzx-launches-milkpowder-futures-103322|title = NZX launches milkpowder futures|date = 4 June 2009 |newspaper = [[National_Business_Review|National Business Review]] |accessdate = 30 September 2011 |agency = [[NZPA|NZPA]] |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141118034536/http://www.nbr.co.nz/article/nzx-launches-milkpowder-futures-103322 |archive-date = 2014-11-18 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>，收入超過172億[[紐西蘭元|新西蘭元]]<ref name="AnnualReport102">{{cite web|url = http://www.fonterra.com/wps/wcm/connect/c7b664804472baa7945edeb7b0c23ace/Fonterra+Annual+Report+2010.pdf?MOD=AJPERES&CACHEID=c7b664804472baa7945edeb7b0c23ace|title = Fonterra Annual Report 2010|accessdate = 5 February 2011|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101215102048/http://fonterra.com/wps/wcm/connect/c7b664804472baa7945edeb7b0c23ace/Fonterra+Annual+Report+2010.pdf?MOD=AJPERES&CACHEID=c7b664804472baa7945edeb7b0c23ace|archivedate = 2010年12月15日}}</ref>，是新西蘭最大的公司。

其名Fonterra來自[[拉丁语|拉丁語]]''fron de terra''，意思是“來自土地的[[泉|泉水]]。”<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.fonterra.com/nz/en/about/company+overview|title = Company overview|accessdate = 28 August 2014|publisher = Fonterra Co-operative Group|archive-date = 2012-10-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121001235802/http://www.fonterra.com/nz/en/About/Company+Overview|dead-url = yes}}</ref>

== 沿革 ==
19世紀時，紐西蘭的乳製品事業開始發展；1882年，當地業者藉由冷凍運送技術第一次輸出奶油到遠在北半球的倫敦。1930年，生產乳品的工廠已經分布於紐西蘭的許多小鎮。

1963年，紐西蘭乳品公會正式成立；2000年，紐西蘭兩大主要乳製品供應商New Zealand Dairy Group和Kiwi Cooperative Dairies負責出口紐西蘭的乳品到全世界。
2001年，紐西蘭三大乳品公司Kiwi Cooperative Dairies、New Zealand Dairy Group 和The New Zealand Dairy Board合併成為恆天然乳品公司（{{Lang-en|Fonterra Brands Holdings Pte. Ltd}}），並於2006年公司整合旗下所有事業體後成立恆天然乳品集團（{{Lang-en|'''Fonterra Co-operative Group Limited'''}}）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.newyoung.com.tw/index.php?node=fonterra|title=恆天然-Fonterra|accessdate=2016-12-08|last=奈思網頁計公司|work=新加坡商永紐股份有限公司台灣分公司|archive-date=2020-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810081734/https://www.newyoung.com.tw/index.php?node=fonterra|dead-url=no}}</ref>

